---
title: Roasted Chickpea and Cauliflower Salad with a lemon yoghurt dressing
description: Fluffy couscous, crispy chickpeas, roasted cauliflower and a creamy lemon dressing, this is a salad that won't leave you wanting more. With an abundant amount of ingredients and flavours, there's certainly something for everyone in this nutritious veggie dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R14_W50_IE_IEXQVV17477-3_Main_high-52742f63.jpg
